99f88f15c5febbca2d13b5b5fda27b844153bf1a.commitMessage:
Rename core module to server (#28180)

This is related to #27933. It renames the core module to server. This is
the first step towards introducing an elasticsearch-core jar.

56540281a868f6b68be2da11749fe67b58d16dd8.commitMessage:
Avoid NPE when getting build information

When the Elasticsearch code is loaded in an unusual classloading
environment (e.g., when using the high-level REST client) in Jetty, the
code source can be null and we trip with an NPE. This commit addresses
this.

Relates #27442

7b68d44ddf2e6522d2b2aa1efead9ccc8b4ef224.commitMessage:
Read Elasticsearch manifest via URL

This commit modifies reading the Elasticsearch jar manifest via the URL
instead of converting the URL to an NIO path for increased portability.

Relates #18999
